<p>Maybe I didn&#8217;t fully understand him (I wasn&#8217;t taking notes), and he certainly is better versed in the issues at hand than everyone else who was in that auditorium combined. But nationalizing the Internet is bad idea. (I can&#8217;t believe I even have to say this). It would set a horrible precedent, would undermine confidence in the American economy, and would be difficult to pull off. </p>
