<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.wix.com">Wix</a>, the browser-based designer that lets users create Flash-based widgets and full-scale webpages, has launched in public beta. The site specializes in creating colorful Flash pages without requiring any coding, and seems to appeal most to &#8220;MySpacers&#8221; looking to add some flair to their sites (Wix does have some more professional templates for businesses). You can see our original review of the site <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.techcrunch.com/2008/04/25/wix-the-bold-web-content-creator/">here</a>.</p>
